EN: The use of diesel vehicles leads to higher energy consumption.

ZH: 新技术的应用可以提高能源开发的效率。
EN: The application of new technologies can improve energy development efficiency.

ZH: 燃煤电厂是一种常见的能源来源。
EN: Coal-fired power plants are a common source of energy.

ZH: 少数国家拥有丰富的天然气能源资源。
EN: Some countries have abundant natural gas energy resources.

ZH: 节约能源是一个全球性的挑战。
EN: Energy conservation is a global challenge.

ZH: 改变个人的能源消耗习惯可以影响整个社会。
EN: Changing individual energy consumption habits can influence the entire society.

ZH: 有必要发展清洁和可持续的能源技术。
EN: It is necessary to develop clean and sustainable energy technologies.
